{"tid":389151,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有個畫家好似中華英雄","createTime":"2017-09-06T04:06:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-18T06:06:07.000Z","uid":12796,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d6ad21971e050b5c7398e32f6eb61ea4e4711ed1","tid":389151,"uid":12796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T04:06:03.000Z","msg":"利申: 非打手<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/06/111202_7fdc1a630c238af0815181f9faa190f5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F06%2F111202_7fdc1a630c238af0815181f9faa190f5.jpg&h=45283b96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一直都想學下畫呢種水墨畫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n於是係google搵咗下 見到原來有個幾出名嘅人畫嘅<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/06/111538_7ffd0141a2daa5348f12c6e94a3c4639.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F06%2F111538_7ffd0141a2daa5348f12c6e94a3c4639.jpg&h=5ece5abf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/06/111544_152530c8eeccb519a38f5269ce36f62e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F06%2F111544_152530c8eeccb519a38f5269ce36f62e.jpg&h=72f8bf93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n睇落又幾似中華英雄<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搵兩搵原來佢叫蔡啟仁 仲同成龍同期拎過傑青<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原來仲有開班教學生 係facebook仲見到佢啲學生都開埋畫展<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Chois-Concept-329725494551/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FChois-Concept-329725494551%2F&d=E2yCoEQOH8xopYD9uxQ%2Fpv7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=de33c825\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Chois-Concept-329725494551/</a><br />\n唔知有冇巴打係佢學生呢<br />\n如果有嘅話 可唔可以同蔡博士講聲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">欠債還錢呀仆街</span></strong></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢條仆街周圍用送畫名義去財仔借錢<br />\n跟住叫佢還錢又係咁拖<br />\n畫展又識開 錢又唔識還<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/06/113334_e53e0bfae9ffad24fd49acee89479243.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F06%2F113334_e53e0bfae9ffad24fd49acee89479243.jpg&h=5c9243f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/06/113337_1300683501c30e7aeededa2172f83786.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F06%2F113337_1300683501c30e7aeededa2172f83786.jpg&h=24f42eeb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nbtw 巴打覺得佢啲畫值唔值幾萬蚊 如果值錢就唔追了 等佢死咗拎去賣算<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c3abe3ec5294d0db6b5f95ab9ea54a2af88a082","tid":389151,"uid":12796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T04:22:34.000Z","msg":"有冇巴打想同中華英雄學兩招<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fef4b7de4eff1b1695a82e8d3d3c90bb0137b87c","tid":389151,"uid":12796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T04:59:05.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"238d844840f404a32c9622d3d410ba4b6d4e0b0a","tid":389151,"uid":12796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T05:52:48.000Z","msg":"無人識佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"381c582102a782e5bfe55b89d9ddf050088d2e46","tid":389151,"uid":56498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T06:16:42.000Z","msg":"咁廢撚有人識咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鳩揮幾筆係人都得"},{"pid":"9886b36472a24b06b854ce6244eda0453d87a537","tid":389151,"uid":12796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T07:51:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁廢撚有人識咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鳩揮幾筆係人都得</blockquote><br />\n求其揮幾筆就借到幾萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9606ec2170888fa7cbf080ac1620d1f9b4ef0a60","tid":389151,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T07:55:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"887915b56941dade0183b5d83759292b0f7d7c3d","tid":389151,"uid":56498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T08:03:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不嬲畫壇都多濕鳩<br />\n<br />\n扮撚晒藝術家<br />\n<br />\n人格低賤</blockquote><br />\n洗黑錢既野"},{"pid":"8a5766b610e42806f8c50e6b2903f5a6cc2b0516","tid":389151,"uid":12796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T08:06:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不嬲畫壇都多濕鳩<br />\n<br />\n扮撚晒藝術家<br />\n<br />\n人格低賤</blockquote><br />\n叫佢還錢時<br />\n佢就拎啲中華小姐傳單出嚟話可以介紹啲囡俾人識<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6b94e4b5603ef437a3b52d9e13d914252299137","tid":389151,"uid":12796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T07:42:28.000Z","msg":"原來已經好多財務公司交俾收數公司搵佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d84b426c1fedb5ff8a612cda2973c40bde00fe6","tid":389151,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T07:51:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d854be4968ddb0c0ffe5523e2b67e0e18b1fe53","tid":389151,"uid":12796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T11:07:20.000Z","msg":"收到風佢屋企係經營埋旺角模型車店叫車道<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"373514ea87fa8848ed052e6649b979e41a37d416","tid":389151,"uid":12796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T05:30:42.000Z","msg":"有冇巴打要學畫畫或者買模型車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99e4f6478abc357890422a0bbde80818b9878b3b","tid":389151,"uid":66436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T05:48:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb15ccb5c28c6ceb7f507484b2d85f23c770f4c2","tid":389151,"uid":12796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T05:51:08.000Z","msg":"估唔到一代傑青竟然搞成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19c1c632e4aa3a4af30cf5e56e6a81d1bf780f39","tid":389151,"uid":12796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T06:22:21.000Z","msg":"點解傑青啲資料無流出<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93fd16897f829eacbdf6656f1a6e222e953154c9","tid":389151,"uid":54734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T05:18:23.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 借咗你幾錢呀"},{"pid":"5326e3c0debaa63029ce1cd26d313322985cc053","tid":389151,"uid":90863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T05:21:24.000Z","msg":"即係樓主係收數佬？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6fb711004a2f4185c36a82bff998e5ea3effc7c","tid":389151,"uid":12796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T05:57:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 借咗你幾錢呀</blockquote><br />\n我老細借架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 七位數字啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e168febf3f5e7e9fbd6b1fc7ad8e5eab21eeccb8","tid":389151,"uid":12796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T05:58:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>即係樓主係收數佬？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj